Metro’s Cordes’ Contract Extension Has Two-Year Limit, FTD Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-09-22T06:01:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/metro-s-cordes-contract-extension-has-two-year-limit-ftd-says.html
Metro AG (MEO) ’s Chief Executive Officer
Eckhard Cordes will step down in the summer of 2014 at the
latest after the extension of his contract was limited to a
maximum of two years,  Financial Times Deutschland  said today,
citing unidentified people with knowledge of the contract.  To contact the reporter on this story:
